verses.text: We praise you, God, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* praise you: \w we|strong="H3068"\w* would call \w on|strong="H5329"\w* your name and declare your wonders.
‘\w At|strong="H3034"\w* \w the|strong="H3034"\w* time \w I|strong="H8034"\w* choose, \w I|strong="H8034"\w* \w will|strong="H8034"\w* judge fairly.

\w Though|strong="H3588"\w* earth melt \w and|strong="H3947"\w* \w all|strong="H3947"\w* \w her|strong="H3947"\w* inhabitants, \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w who|strong="H3588"\w* \w keep|strong="H3947"\w* steady \w her|strong="H3947"\w* pillars.’ \qs Selah\qs*

\w I|strong="H3605"\w* say \w to|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* boasters, ‘Boast not’; \w to|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* wicked, ‘Lift not \w up|strong="H3427"\w* \w your|strong="H3605"\w* horn:

\w For|strong="H7311"\w* \w not|strong="H1696"\w* from east nor west, \w not|strong="H1696"\w* from desert nor mountains;

\w but|strong="H3588"\w* \w God|strong="H3808"\w* \w himself|strong="H3808"\w* \w is|strong="H4161"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* judge, humbling \w one|strong="H3808"\w* \w and|strong="H4057"\w* exalting \w another|strong="H3808"\w*.

\w In|strong="H2088"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* hand \w of|strong="H8199"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \nd Lord\nd* \w is|strong="H2088"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* cup foaming wine, richly spiced. Out \w of|strong="H8199"\w* \w this|strong="H2088"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* pours \w a|strong="H3068"\w* draught, \w and|strong="H2088"\w* all \w the|strong="H3588"\w* wicked \w of|strong="H8199"\w* earth must drain \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w down|strong="H8213"\w* \w to|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* dregs.

\w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* rejoice \w forever|strong="H3605"\w*, singing \w praise|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* Jacob.

\w I|strong="H5046"\w* \w will|strong="H3290"\w* hew \w all|strong="H5769"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* horns \w of|strong="H5769"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* wicked, \w but|strong="H3290"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* horns \w of|strong="H5769"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* just \w shall|strong="H3290"\w* \w be|strong="H5769"\w* \w lifted|strong="H3290"\w*.
